ase";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:318:"Not far behind the release of HireBee, were just about ready to roll out another app theme. Before doing so, we wanted to leak out this little teaser prior to the official launch later this month. Taskerr allows you to setup and monetize your own micro jobs website. Match job listers with sellers so they [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"David";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2047:"<p><img src="//cdn.appthemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/taskerr-teaser.png" alt="Taskerr theme teaser" width="650" height="454" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8521" /></p>\n<p>Not far behind the release of <a href="http://www.appthemes.com/themes/hirebee/">HireBee</a>, were just about ready to roll out another app theme. Before doing so, we wanted to leak out this little teaser prior to the official launch later this month.</p>\n<p>Taskerr allows you to setup and monetize your own micro jobs website. Match job listers with sellers so they can get small things done at an unbeatable value. You make money by taking a fee from each job. Earning passive income is really that easy!<br />\n<span id="more-8520"></span></p>\n<p>Create a specific niche or go with a broad approach. The sky&#8217;s the limit on whatever micro job service youd like to provide.</p>\n<p>Stay tuned as well be announcing the release in the next couple of weeks!</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=RlNr5nplFXo:4Q-L3cfkqcY:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://f