ans: Recurring Optional A plan that [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Josh Ronk";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4048:"<p>Just when you thought Vantage had all the features that a great WordPress directory theme needed&#8230;here comes another great release with two of the most coveted features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Recurring Payments Support</li>\n<li>Faster and More Powerful Search</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Recurring Payments</h3>\n<p>Now you, as the site owner, have 3 options for your pricing plans:<br />\n<span id="more-7910"></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Recurring Optional\n<ul>\n<li>A plan that offers a recurring option, the user will be allowed to choose whether they want the plan to recur, or just expire at the end of it&#8217;s term.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Forced Recurring\n<ul>\n<li>A plan that recurs, but does not offer the user the option.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Non Recurring\n<ul>\n<li>A plan that just lets the listing expire after the plan&#8217;s set time period. This works like pricing plans always have before.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Create Listing Page &#8211; Showing Recurring and Non-Recurring Pricing Plan Examples</h4>\n<p><img src="//cdn.appthemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/vantage-recurring-payments.png" alt="Vantage 1.3 -  Recurring Payments Support" width="648" style="border: 1px solid #666" class="alignnone size-full" /></p>\n<p>With these new recurring options, you can setup your pricing plans to suit your varying needs, and now your customers will greatly appreciate the convenience that the recurring functionality provides.</p>\n<h3>More Powerful Search</h3>\n<p>Search just got a boost! Now, your searches will complete faster time than ever before and will now be even more thorough! Now, when a user searches for a search term, that term will be searched across the following fields:</p>\n<p><strong>Searches for Listings:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Title\n<ul>\n<li>Now, If your Listing title includes an apostrophe, like for example &#8220;Joe&#8217;s Pizza&#8221;, a search for either &#8220;Joes Pizza&#8221; or &#8220;Joe&#8217;s Pizza&#8221; will return the correct result!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Description</li>\n<li>Categories</li>\n<li>Tags</li>\n<li>Address</li>\n<li>Website URL</li>\n<li>Phone Number</li>\n<li>Facebook</li>\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>&amp; All Custom Form Values!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Searches for Events:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Title\n<ul>\n<li>Now, If your Event title includes an apostrophe, like for example &#8220;Macy&#8217;s Parade&#8221;, a search for either &#8220;Macys Parade&#8221; or &#8220;Macy&#8217;s Parade&#8221; will return the correct result!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Description</li>\n<li>Categories</li>\n<li>Tags</li>\n<li>Event Address</li>\n<li>Event Website URL</li>\n<li>Phone Number</li>\n<li>Event Location Address</li>\n<li>Event Location URL</li>\n<li>Facebook</li>\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>&amp; All Custom Form Values!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There are also many other great smaller features, and bugs fixed. See the <a href="//docs.appthemes.com/vantage/vantage-version-1-3/" target="_blank">Vantage 1.3 Release Notes</a> for further details.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=Yfwu1fUDiFg:JUVBkBw0NzE:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/appthemes/~4/Yfwu1fUDiFg" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"http://www.appthemes.com/blog/vantage-1-3-released/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"8";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://www.appthemes.com/blog/vantage-1-3-released/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:36:"Clipper Powers Celebrity Coupon Site";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/appthemes/~3/ReIbtu1NOyU/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://www.appthemes.com/